---
title: Chili Chili Bang Bang Chicken with Cauliflower Rice & Roasted Broccoli
description: Another work day, another dinner daydream. You know what we mean. You’re sitting at your desk and 2pm rolls around. Suddenly, all you can think is, “Dinner...what the heck am I going to eat for dinner?!” Well, we’ve got you covered. Here’s the plan: crispy panko-crusted chicken, fluffy scallion-flecked rice, and tender roasted broccoli. To finish things off, the chicken is drizzled with a life-affirming ponzu chili mayo. Talk about a dream come true!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/669ed1a646ae2b14647c3ca5-0e3d59c3.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/66a13c9ebbd88d3e9c686e75-en-US.pdf
